data.text:
1. Brittany Murphy 1977 - 2009

2. Early Life Born in Atlanta, Georgia on November 10, 1977 "When I asked my mom to move to California, she sold everything and moved out here for me. ... She always believed in me." Brittany Murphy First starred in movies such as Clueless, Girl Interrupted and Drop Dead Gorgeous

3. Music Was in a band called Blessed Soul in the early 90s In June 2006, Paul Oakenfold released the single "Faster Kill Pussycat" and became hit number one on Billboards Hottest Dance Club Party chart Sang again in the movie Happy Feet in which she covered Queen's Somebody to Love and Earth, Wind and Fire's Boogie Wonderland Also starred in music videos such as; Here by Luscious Jacksons and Closet Thing to Heaven by Tears for Fears
